# CODEOWNERS — declare default reviewers for paths in this repo.
#
# GitHub auto-assigns the matching owner as a reviewer whenever a PR touches
# a path covered by a rule below. Replace the owners with real GitHub handles
# or team handles when you fork this template.
#
# Syntax: <path glob> <space-separated owners>
# Patterns are evaluated bottom-to-top; the last match wins.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-customizations/about-code-owners

# Adopter note
# When you fork this template, replace all @Luis85 handles below with your own
# GitHub user or team handles. Rules without a valid owner are silently ignored
# by GitHub, so invalid handles = no automatic reviewer assignment.

